<title>mḥtạj lk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 mḥtạj lk yạ yswʿ kẖạyf ạ̉nạ wḥdy
 tʿạl wkẖdny mʿạk lrạḥẗ wḥb ạ̉bdy
 mḥtạj lk yạ yswʿ mʿạyạ bạ̹ydyk tsẖfyny
 bạrk ḥyạty qlby kẖṭạyạ wblmsẗ ạḥyyny
 kẖạyf ạ̹blys yyjy yqwlly ạ̹yh ạlly mbkyny
 wạ̉nạ mn ḍʿfy ạ̉qwl rby nạsyny
 fy wsṭ ạlẓlạm bạmsẖy wkẖwfy mạlyny
 ṣrkẖt mn gẖyr klạm ạnqdẖny wnjyny
 mn kl qlby bạqwl tʿạl tʿbt yạ ṭbyby
 sạmʿ nfsy btqwl lạ ttrkny yạ ḥbyby
 hạfḍl ạ̉ṣrkẖ wạ̉bky qdạm ʿrsẖ yswʿy
 hạfḍl hnạ mstny tyjy wtmsḥ dmwʿy
 ạ̉bdaⁿạ msẖ hạstslm ạ̉bdaⁿạ lḍʿf ạ̹ymạny
 wạtẖq fy yswʿ jdaⁿạ jdaⁿạ dạ mạt ʿlsẖạny
 wlmạ ạ̹blys ysạ̉lny ạ̹yh ạlly mbkyny
 hạtrd nfsy ạlḍʿyfẗ wtqwl rby hạysẖfyny</lyrics>
